<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٦]</span> بَابٌ تَحْذِيفُ الْوَجْهِ وَنَتْفِهِ وَحَلْقُ الْقَفَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٦٢-<span class="c5"> أَخْبَرَنَا أَبُو بَكْرٍ الْمَرْوَزِيُّ قَالَ:</span> قُلْتُ لِأَبِي عَبْدِ اللَّهِ:<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَمَا تَرَى فِي تَحْذِيفِ الْوَجْهِ؟<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>⦗١٢٤⦘<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ:</span> أَمَّا الْوَجْهُ فَالْمِقْرَاضُ يَأْتِي عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>